<h1>Social Integration</h1>
<p>You can link Facebook, Twitter, and LinkedIn accounts to your Hipsell account.  Links to these will show up on your profile.</p>

<h3>Accounts You've Linked</h3>
<p>
{{#fb}}
  <a href="{{& fb}}" target="_blank">Facebook</a>
{{/fb}}
{{#twitter}}
  <a href="{{& twitter}}" target="_blank">Twitter</a>
{{/twitter}}
{{#linkedin}}
  <a href="{{& linkedin}}" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a>
{{/linkedin}}
</p>

<h3>Link an Account</h3>
<p>
{{^fb}}
  <a href="{{& server}}/fb/connect?">Facebook</a>
{{/fb}}
{{^twitter}}
  <a href="{{& server}}/twitter/connect?" target="_blank">Twitter</a>
{{/twitter}}
{{^linkedin}}
  <a href="{{& server}}/linkedin/connect?" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a>
{{/linkedin}}
</p>
